Package: bsvarPost
Type: Package
Title: Post-Estimation Tools for 'bsvars' and 'bsvarSIGNs'
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("David", "Zenz", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "office@davidzenz.com")
Description: Companion post-estimation tools for Bayesian structural vector
    autoregressions fitted with the 'bsvars' and 'bsvarSIGNs' packages.
    Provides tidy extractors for impulse responses, cumulative dynamic
    multipliers, forecast error variance decompositions, historical
    decompositions, shocks, and forecasts; cross-package cumulative dynamic
    multiplier estimation via cdm(); model comparison utilities; posterior
    hypothesis testing and joint inference; representative model selection;
    response-shape summaries; acceptance diagnostics for sign-restricted
    models; and a 'ggplot2' plotting and publication-reporting layer built
    on top of existing posterior objects.
